        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_27gc' title='Col. 27GC &mdash; HL Deb 29 June 1999 vol 603 c27GC' name='column_27gc' href='#column_27gc' rel='bookmark'>27GC</a>
        appeal. To allow such powers to a conservation body without the right of appeal would be contrary to natural justice. I beg to move.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0603P0-01622'>
        <a name='S5LV0603P0_19990629_GCR_103'>  </a>
