        <q>Page 5, line 4, leave out ("or adjacent to")</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0603P0-01715'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0603P0_19990629_GCR_196' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
