          <p class='first-para'>
            The noble Lord, Lord Renton of Mount Harry, has spoken to this amendment very fully and I need say little more, other than to support him.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0603P0-01723'>
